-- Ex-Argentine Minister Cavallo Joins GlobalSource Partners in Buenos Aires
-- B y   D r e w   B e n s o n
-- 2010-10-25T21:30:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/ex-argentine-minister-cavallo-joins-globalsource-partners-in-buenos-aires.html
Former Argentine Economy Minister
Domingo Cavallo has joined GlobalSource Partners in Buenos
Aires.  “Dr. Cavallo will bring his broad experience and deep
economic insight to the ongoing delivery of our monthly and
quarterly updates as well as Market Briefs, addressing market-
moving events,” New York-based GlobalSource said in a statement
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Drew Benson  in Buenos Aires at 
 abenson9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
